Installation
------------
Enter the following command to build executable gravicappa-wm:
make

Running gravicappa-wm
---------------------
See included sample/dotxinitrc which shows possible way of running
window manager. Those commands can be added into your .xinitrc.

gravicappa-wm reads ~/.uwm.scm configuration file which is usual
scheme source. Sample can be taken from sample/dotuwm.scm.
